(408, 1, '2014-01-20 00:50:56', '2014-01-20 00:50:56', 'Welcome to our first annual Bradfordlicious Festival!\r\n\r\n<img class="alignright" alt="food-1388709_83105273-420x279" src="http://www.bradfordlicious.com//wp-content/uploads/2013/12/food-1388709_83105273-420x279.jpg" width="420" height="279" />\r\n\r\nGet ready Bradford West Gwillimbury for our first year of gourmet gastronomy with Bradfordlicious <i>2014</i>. It is the only festival in Bradford West Gwillimbury that invites you to enjoy the tastes and sounds one of your favourite restaurants ~ and try several new ones! We have worked hard to ensure you''ll have a great experience and travel the world in culinary style. Best of all, it’s far cheaper than flying... and there''s no full-body scan! With 15 restaurants participating in our first event, each with it’s own unique, delicious fixed-menu options to offer, you’ll be pleasantly satisfied!\r\n\r\n<i>Three Course Dinner Menu is to be chosen from a select menu at each restaurant. Prices do not include applicable taxes, alcohol or additional menu items. Please contact the restaurants in advance for reservations. Ask about select menu.</i>', 'Restaurants', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-20 00:50:56', '2014-01-20 00:50:56', '', 21, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=408', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
