(295, 1, '2014-04-11 16:25:34', '2014-04-11 16:25:34', '[details address="" latitude="" longitude="" phone="" hours="" website="www.bigmommas.goldbook.ca"]\n\nIt’s Jamaica without the Beach. <span style="line-height: 1.5em;">This restaurant is an absolute jewel in the middle of downtown Bradford West Gwillimbury.</span>\n\n<span style="line-height: 1.5em;">A warm welcome from the owner and authentic Jamaican menu. The food is </span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">wonderful with generous portions and lots of specials to choose from, including </span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Jamaican drinks. The food is served in a great ambiance with Reggae being played </span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">in the background.</span>\n\nAlthough not obvious from the main road, the restaurant is <span style="line-height: 1.5em;">frequented by plenty of locals who flock to the place. The menu is priced very </span><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">reasonably. A must if you are in the area or just passing through.</span>', 'Big Momma''s', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '153-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-04-11 16:25:34', '2014-04-11 16:25:34', '', 153, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=295', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
