(402, 1, '2014-01-20 00:37:47', '2014-01-20 00:37:47', 'It’s Jamaica without the Beach\r\nThis restaurant is an absolute jewel in the middle of downtown BWG.\r\nA warm welcome from the owner and authentic Jamaican menu. The food is\r\nwonderful with generous portions and lots of specials to choose from, including\r\nJamaican drinks. The food is served in a great ambiance with Reggae being played\r\nin the background. Although not obvious from the main road, the restaurant is\r\nfrequented by plenty of locals who flock to the place. The menu is priced very\r\nreasonably. A must if you are in the area or just passing through.', 'Big Momma''s', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '153-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-20 00:37:47', '2014-01-20 00:37:47', '', 153, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=402', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
