willimbury">Bradford West Gwillimbury</a>, south <a title="Innisfil, Ontario" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Innisfil,_Ontario">Innisfil</a> and <a title="Holland Marsh" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holland_Marsh">Holland Marsh</a> areas for over 18 years – covering local Town Council, charity and cultural events, sports and business news. It is delivered free by carrier, throughout its distribution area.\r\n\r\nBradfordlicious 2014 is proudly sponsored by the Bradford Times. Their partnership helps make this inargural event a wonderful success.\r\n\r\nTo connect with us, please visit our website at: <a href="http://www.bradfordtimes.ca">http://www.bradfordtimes.ca</a>', 'Sponsors', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '224-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-20 03:04:24', '2014-01-20 03:04:24', '', 224, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com//?p=418', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
