(870, 1, '2015-01-26 05:38:29', '2015-01-26 05:38:29', 'Let a team with over 25 years of combined experience in the hospitality industry provide you top-shelf service in what we love to do! A group of dynamic hospitality industry leaders came together in 2012 to create 1812 GrillHouse. The demand for innovative event solutions outside of the GTA as well as the desire for successful events in the social and private sectors became the focus of our company. As a client of 1812 GrillHouse, you will be immersed in the top talent this town has to offer that will create a memorable experience with unparalleled service. A completely seamless execution will provide you with a professional event filled with sophistication, flare and uniqueness.\r\n<h1></h1>', '1812 Grillhouse', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '157-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-26 05:38:29', '2015-01-26 05:38:29', '', 157, 'http://www.bradfordlicious.com/157-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
